arStrings.szText:
Critically Striking with an {c_important}Earth{/c} Skill makes you go on a rampage for {c_number}{SF_6}{/c} seconds, causing your {c_important}Werebear{/c} form to deal {c_number}{payload:DAMAGE}{/c} to Nearby enemies every {c_number}[SF_4|1|]{/c} seconds.

Overpowering with a {c_important}Werebear{/c} Skill increases the damage of your {c_important}Earth{/c} Skills by {c_number}[SF_1 * 100|%x|]{/c} for {c_number}{SF_6}{/c} seconds.
While in Werebear form, deal damage to Nearby enemies.
